snippet.title: Famicom Disk System - Jikai Shounen Mettomag (1987)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Jikai Shounen Mettomag is a Puzzle game, developed by Thinking Rabbit and published by SquareSoft, which was released in Japan in 1987.
